sequenceDiagram
  participant T as Technician
  participant Tool as hvb_factory_tui
  participant Board as Board (Modbus)

  T->>Tool: hvb_factory_tui -p /dev/ttyUSB0
  Tool->>Board: connect
  Tool-->>T: "Connected to /dev/ttyUSB0 ..."

  T->>Tool: cal unlock
  Tool->>Board: unlock step 1 + step 2, enter Calibration Mode
  Tool-->>T: "Calibration session started"

  loop for each channel to calibrate
    T->>Tool: cal ch <n>
    T->>Tool: cal enable

    loop at least 2 DAC points
      T->>Tool: cal dac <code>
      T->>Tool: cal sample
      Tool->>Board: sample + read raw ADC
      Tool-->>T: dac / adc_v / adc_i
      T->>T: read external reference meter
    end

    T->>T: compute k, b offline (linear fit)

    T->>Tool: cal coeff out <k> <b>
    T->>Tool: cal coeff meas-v <k> <b>
    T->>Tool: cal coeff meas-i <k> <b>
    T->>Tool: cal coeff show
    Tool-->>T: confirm K/B per axis

    T->>Tool: cal disable
    T->>Tool: cal commit
    Tool->>Board: save coefficients to NVS
  end

  T->>Tool: cal exit-cal
  Tool->>Board: restore previous operating mode
